WEBVTT

00:00:01.702 --> 00:00:06.082
You ungrateful...

00:00:06.186 --> 00:00:10.775
You did this to yourself.
You said fewer clients.

00:00:10.983 --> 00:00:14.424
How do you think it feels
firing you?

00:00:14.633 --> 00:00:19.951
I've thought about it all week.
Get past yourself for a second!

00:00:20.159 --> 00:00:23.289
- You'll lose.
- You wanted smaller.

00:00:23.497 --> 00:00:28.398
Well, now I want all my clients,
and yours, too.

